tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Requests" FROM usersession where useraction.application="MyApp" MyFilter and StepFunnel1

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Satisfied Sessions" from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp" MyFilter and userExperienceScore="SATISFIED" and (StepFunnel1)

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Satisfied Conversions" from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp" MyFilter and userExperienceScore="SATISFIED" and LastFunnelStep and (StepFunnel1)

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Satisfied Not Converted" from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp" MyFilter and userExperienceScore="SATISFIED" and not LastFunnelStep and (StepFunnel1)
